Andaz Liverpool Street is built on the site of the Bethlehem Hospital which housed the mentally ill . 
 Dating back to 1247, most people will know the institution by the name 'bedlam'These days it's a swanky celebrity-baiting hotel with 267 rooms and celebrity guests including Beyonce and Lil Kim . 
 Four of the king rooms are decorated with mesmerising murals created by artists . 
